"Praktik terbaik kebersihan kredensial untuk admin dan operator penggajian."

#: home/templates/home/security.html:1270
msgid ""
"Secure onboarding and access setup aligned to your organisational structure."
msgstr ""
"Orientasi aman dan pengaturan akses yang selaras dengan struktur organisasi "
"Anda."

#: home/templates/home/security.html:1276
msgid "Credential controls"
msgstr "Kontrol kredensial"

#: home/templates/home/security.html:1277
msgid ""
"MFA, strong password policies, and least-privilege access baked into daily "
"operations."
msgstr ""
"MFA, kebijakan kata sandi yang kuat, dan akses hak istimewa minimum "
"terintegrasi ke dalam operasi sehari-hari."

#: home/templates/home/security.html:1280
msgid "Operational safeguards"
msgstr "Perlindungan operasional"

#: home/templates/home/security.html:1281
msgid ""
"Approval workflows and traceability to reduce errors and prevent "
"unauthorised changes."
msgstr ""
"Alur kerja persetujuan dan kemampuan telusur untuk mengurangi kesalahan dan "
"mencegah perubahan yang tidak sah."

#: home/templates/home/security.html:1284
msgid "Security culture"
msgstr "Budaya keamanan"

#: home/templates/home/security.html:1285
msgid "Shared responsibility—your team + our platform + our experts."
msgstr "Tanggung jawab bersama — tim Anda + platform kami + para ahli kami."

#: home/templates/home/security.html:1296
msgid "Want a deeper security walkthrough?"
msgstr "Ingin panduan keamanan yang lebih dalam?"

#: home/templates/home/security.html:1298
msgid ""
"Talk to our team about your footprint, data residency needs, and access "
"model — and we’ll map the right security posture for your cross-border "
"payroll operations."
msgstr ""
"Bicaralah dengan tim kami tentang jejak Anda, kebutuhan residensi data, dan "
"model akses — dan kami akan memetakan postur keamanan yang tepat untuk "
"operasi penggajian lintas batas Anda."

